1. Video longer than 10 sec

Handled by:

Timer(Duration(seconds: 10))

We force stop, not wait for video end.

2. Memory leaks (critical)

We explicitly:

_videoController?.dispose();
_timer?.cancel();
3. API fails

Right now:

Logs error
Doesn’t crash

You can improve with retry if needed.

4. Black screen before video init

Handled via:

CircularProgressIndicator()
